      "title": "No need to queue up at petrol sheds: Bowser Assn.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "There is no use of queuing for petrol as stocks of fuel in hand with Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CPC) storage facilities have fun out, The Ceylon Petroleum Private Bowser Owners Association (CPPBOA) said.",
        "They said there will be no fuel transportation taking place until Monday due to weekend holidays.",
        "Nevertheless, diesel will be transport from tomorrow but not petrol, they said.",
        "They said only 1000MT of petrol remaining at CPC storage to be used during emergency situation.(CS)"
